### DSyoubrew Homebrew Projects Site
Welcome To The DSyoubrew Homebrew Site! This Site Features Projects That We Are Working On.
### Homebrew Info
DSyoubrew Developes Games Exclusive For Homebrew. Homebrew Can Be Downloaded Using boot.3dsx.
### How To Load
Home-brew Launcher Checks The Whole SD Card For Files. When You Place A 3DSX File In The SD Card. It Will Show Up.
Loading Homebrew Is Very Easy. Though You Need A boot.3dsx File To Load It. The Current Way Is Browserhax And Themehax
